## üìè 3. Spacing System

Follows Tailwind‚Äôs default spacing scale with minor extensions. All spacing should be in `rem`-based utility classes.

| Name  | Value (rem) | Class     |
|-------|--------------|-----------|
| XS    | 0.25rem      | `p-1`     |
| SM    | 0.5rem       | `p-2`     |
| MD    | 1rem         | `p-4`     |
| LG    | 1.5rem       | `p-6`     |
| XL    | 2rem         | `p-8`     |

Use grid-based spacing for layout elements:
```html
<div class="grid gap-6 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
```

